00:09:37.994 --> 00:09:39.579
<font color="white">-Man. I'm busy.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-I'm sorry. sir.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

172
00:09:39.662 --> 00:09:40.997
<font color="white">In any case!</font><font color="white"></font>

173
00:09:42.456 --> 00:09:45.042
<font color="white">When I hit the switch.</font><font color="white">
